{"tid":1804001,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2019 韓國女星IG人氣王揭曉！IU、太妍都不敵性感夯團，冠軍追蹤人數比台灣總人口還多","createTime":"2019-12-30T15:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T05:44:06.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9c14781047ea8244c4ebbaad7bda052ac57e2b2c","tid":1804001,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:44:46.000Z","msg":"2019即將結束，也是各項榜單「算總帳」的時候，其中大受關注的韓國女星 IG 人氣王，今年看頭也不小，性感夯團 BLACKPINK 不但再度全員入榜，且前4名都是她們！位居榜首的「她」，追蹤總人數更是比台灣總人口還要多！<br />\n<br />\n這份榜單以有開設個人帳號的女星為主，像是周子瑜所在的夯團 TWICE 也有1120萬追蹤粉絲，不少粉絲就敲碗，希望她們成立個人帳號呢！<br />\n<br />\nTop10：朴信惠&rarr;1010萬<br />\n幾乎每部主演的戲劇都是收視率保證的朴信惠，上一檔《阿爾罕布拉宮的回憶》在去年底播出橫跨到2019年初，之後大大小小活動不斷，也維持了活躍度。而她目前正在拍攝新劇中，令粉絲相當期待。<br />\n<br />\nTop9：潤娥&rarr;1050萬<br />\n去年拿下第4名的潤娥，今年雖然掉到第9名，憑著出眾的外貌與演技，本來就吸粉無數，但令人意外的潤娥私下超親民又可愛，難怪至今聲勢不墜。<br />\n<br />\nTop8：秀智&rarr;1134萬<br />\n清純的臉蛋、穠纖合度的身材，讓秀智在韓國有著「國民初戀」的封號。經常在社群上分享自己的真實生活，加上今年也有新作品《VAGABOND》上映，活躍度整年滿滿。<br />\n<br />\nTop7：IU&rarr;1138萬<br />\n同樣追蹤人數超過1130萬的IU，以些微人數勝出。今年可以說是IU大紅的一年！從《德魯那酒店》席捲，到推出新專輯、辦巡迴演唱，一整年都是IU的話題呢！<br />\n<br />\nTop6：泫雅&rarr;1240萬<br />\n性感著稱的泫雅，今年也是活動滿滿，不但推出了新專輯、辦演唱會，更是常常在IG分享生活。私下的泫雅其實「很少女」，不化妝時的她看起來更像是大學生呢！"},{"pid":"509a386e0581760f80e0fd5c258f22c3c01a6f33","tid":1804001,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:44:53.000Z","msg":"Top5：太妍&rarr;1410萬<br />\n少女時代成員太妍，去年拿下冠軍，今年因活動較少掉到第5名，但還是有超過1410萬追蹤數。其實太妍非常會穿搭，本身算嬌小的她經常透過衣著穿出模特兒般的好比例，難怪人氣始終旺。"},{"pid":"e13d9e915ea4af9d331230796792525ee1a7fa7e","tid":1804001,"uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:45:05.000Z","msg":"Top4：BLACKPINK Jisoo&rarr;1970萬<br />\n韓國夯團 BLACKPINK 真的太誇張了！從第4名開始包榜。拿下第4的是出道就獲得「怪物新人」封號的 Jisoo，因團員身材各個都太耀眼，她被評為是「最無殺傷力」的，但好身材加上甜美笑容，依舊吸粉無數。"},{"pid":"9750c6928d6de20d63f63e45ce15339632147cac","tid":1804001,"uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:45:15.000Z","msg":"Top3：BLACKPINK Ros&eacute;&rarr;2100百萬<br />\nBLACKPINK 中具有獨特嗓音的 Ros&eacute;，加上火辣的身材和精緻的臉孔，完全就是殺手等級。擁有19吋螞蟻腰的她，穿搭也非常有型，就連簡單的T恤、衛衣都能穿出風格，難怪粉絲超愛。"},{"pid":"38a9f859638a2a0f26dc4cfeaafadbfb3e16072d","tid":1804001,"uid":305536,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:45:19.000Z","msg":"<ins>德國聯署</ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=87e1944d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=dc17c40c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n<br />\n3. 暫時最後一個 deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">1/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要29000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=a9675020\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>美國聯署</ins> deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">3/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要7000人 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhelp-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=2a22a86c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">deadline fighters 請出招</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47983d7538258d9093a90c87a87cda53777a300d","tid":1804001,"uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:45:28.000Z","msg":"Top2：BLACKPINK Jennie&rarr;2310萬<br />\n有「人間香奈兒」之稱的 Jennie，因時尚品味獨到，完全就是品牌最愛！加上姣好臉蛋與身材，代言活動接不完，無論私服穿搭或公開場合，只要一站出來就是超吸睛呢！"},{"pid":"d72948d304ddc047abe46773822450ea13ad02d6","tid":1804001,"uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":10,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:45:38.000Z","msg":"Top1：BLACKPINK Lisa&rarr;2790萬<br />\n有著完美的九頭身比例，被封為「人間芭比」的 Lisa，是2019年韓國女星的IG人氣王！長相精緻的她也擁有逆天好身材，不只經常分享穿搭，也經常分享美妝、保養、和生活的話題，隨便一站都是一道風景的她，冠軍實至名歸！"},{"pid":"a3fd1424a4bf2521d91a7f677c6f346afbfee787","tid":1804001,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:46:31.000Z","msg":"我地黑粉尾能到..."},{"pid":"56d67e2f52ba101ba2599bed47dc8208c3870b31","tid":1804001,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/372627f29f619f5f5b93ad727a90ad26/31dddcc155aa450d-b4/s500x750/7255757a1239c222a5ccf70805f829fd051c4e6c.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F372627f29f619f5f5b93ad727a90ad26%2F31dddcc155aa450d-b4%2Fs500x750%2F7255757a1239c222a5ccf70805f829fd051c4e6c.gifv&h=f252abf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/74c988be1c547ffa3f6587539f7922a1/31dddcc155aa450d-5a/s500x750/eedc6fbd254f2fff6aef0f2623e70d26b55514a1.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbna